                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <p>
                            Although you do not need an attorney to file a claim under the DBA, having an experienced
                            attorney’s help can prove invaluable. Not only can an experienced attorney help guide you
                            through the DBA process, helping you avoid costly pitfalls and delays, but he or she can also
                            help you overcome any objections that the insurer may raise.
